Installation
In the folder above your project root:
>> composer create-project codeigniter4/appstarter project-root
------------ ALl An Important Commands -------------------------------------

1. Create a Controller: 
   >> php spark make:controller MyController

2. Create a Model:
   >> php spark make:model MyModel

3. Create a View:
   >> php spark make:view my_view

4. Create a Migration:
   >> php spark make:migration create_users_table

5. Run Migrations:
   >> php spark migrate

6. Rollback Last Migration:   
   >> php spark migrate:rollback

7. Create a Seeder:
   >> php spark make:seeder UsersSeeder

8. Run Seeders:
   >> php spark db:seed

9. List Available Routes:
   >> php spark routes
10. Serve the Application Locally:   
    >> php spark routes

11. Clear Cache:
    >> php spark cache:clear

12. Generate Documentation for Routes:
    >> php spark routes:discover

13. Create a Filter:
    >> php spark make:filter MyFilter

14. Create a Namespace:
    >>  php spark make:namespace MyNamespace

15. Create a Command:
    >> php spark make:command MyCommand

16. Publish Core Files:
    >> php spark publish

17. Publish Assets:
    >> php spark publish:assets

18. Publish Migrations:
    >> php spark publish:migrations

19. Publish Models:
    >> php spark publish:models

20. Publish Views:
    >> php spark publish:views

21. Help (for Help on a Specific Command):
    >> php spark help make:controller

These are some of the most commonly used commands in CodeIgniter 4. You can access a full list of commands by running php spark list in your terminal. Each command has its specific usage and options, which you can explore by appending --help to the command. For example:

>> php spark make:controller --help

C:\Users\sanja\Documents\project-root>php spark make:controller --help

CodeIgniter v4.5.2 Command Line Tool - Server Time: 2024-06-13 05:30:50 UTC+00:00

Usage:
  make:controller <name> [options]

Description:
  Generates a new controller file.

Arguments:
  name  The controller class name.

Options:
  --bare       Extends from CodeIgniter\Controller instead of BaseController.
  --restful    Extends from a RESTful resource, Options: [controller, presenter]. Default: "controller".
  --namespace  Set root namespace. Default: "APP_NAMESPACE".
  --suffix     Append the component title to the class name (e.g. User => UserController).
  --force      Force overwrite existing file.

-----------------------------------------------
--version

CodeIgniter v4.5.2 Command Line Tool - Server Time: 2024-06-13 07:31:02 UTC+00:00

Cache
  cache:clear       Clears the current system caches.
  cache:info        Shows file cache information in the current system.

CodeIgniter
  config:check      Check your Config values.
  env               Retrieves the current environment, or set a new one.
  filter:check      Check filters for a route.
  help              Displays basic usage information.
  list              Lists the available commands.
  namespaces        Verifies your namespaces are setup correctly.
  optimize          Optimize for production.
  phpini:check      Check your php.ini values.
  publish           Discovers and executes all predefined Publisher classes.
  routes            Displays all routes.
  serve             Launches the CodeIgniter PHP-Development Server.

Database
  db:create         Create a new database schema.
  db:seed           Runs the specified seeder to populate known data into the database.
  db:table          Retrieves information on the selected table.
  migrate           Locates and runs all new migrations against the database.
  migrate:refresh   Does a rollback followed by a latest to refresh the current state of the database.
  migrate:rollback  Runs the "down" method for all migrations in the last batch.
  migrate:status    Displays a list of all migrations and whether they've been run or not.

Encryption
  key:generate      Generates a new encryption key and writes it in an `.env` file.

Generators
  make:cell         Generates a new Controlled Cell file and its view.
  make:command      Generates a new spark command.
  make:config       Generates a new config file.
  make:controller   Generates a new controller file.
  make:entity       Generates a new entity file.
  make:filter       Generates a new filter file.
  make:migration    Generates a new migration file.
  make:model        Generates a new model file.
  make:scaffold     Generates a complete set of scaffold files.
  make:seeder       Generates a new seeder file.
  make:test         Generates a new test file.
  make:validation   Generates a new validation file.

Housekeeping
  debugbar:clear    Clears all debugbar JSON files.
  logs:clear        Clears all log files.

Translation
  lang:find         Find and save available phrases to translate.

